title: Class Garden

originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Yo soy Polar

title: The Curse of Elmore

title: The Search Engine
description: On a mission to recover a pair of fuzzy dice from the junkyard, Tig and Seek battle it out with Boss' brand-new robot, Search Engine, to prove they're the better finders.

title: Horror Club

title: Haunted RV
description: After Uncle Grandpa's Haunted House spirals out of control, the gang must save the teenagers stuck inside.

title: #MisgivingTree
description: Jessica Cruz and Pam Isley bond over protecting an ancient tree from being cut down. Neither of them realizes who the other's alter ego is, or the lengths to which they'll go to protect what's important.

title: Hollywood Knights!
description: When Scooby and the gang are investigating one of the most haunted mansions in the historic Hollywood Hills, they meet up with none-other than famous actor George Takei. His house is next door, and he's hoping to save this abandoned, old mansion as a historic landmark. As an old suit of armor comes alive and chases them all over the spooky estate, the gang and Mr. Takei discover the mansion is not as abandoned as everyone thought.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: Get the Egg Home
description: When an egg blows down into the village, it is Mush-Mush and friends' mission to return it to Mush Mountain. Two problems though: there is a Beetle Boom on and all the beetles try to charge and knock over Mushables, and Lilit has always wanted to see an egg hatch so secretly drags her feet.

title: Ghost Princess

title: Showdown At Mayahuel Garden
description: When Victor, Valentino, Charlene and Pineapple get separated from their grandmothers, Chata and Maria Teresa are forced to put aside their rivalry and work together to reunite with their grandchildren.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: The Eater

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: Unconventional Dolphinism

title: Let's Be Friends

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain

When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

description: Stevonnie se encuentra solo en una aventura.

title: Seamos Amigos

originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Malgax Attacks
description: Ben finally manages to rid himself of Skurd... just when he needs the Slime-Biot most.

title: Bubblevicious/The Bare Facts

When she sets out to prove she's hardcore, she takes everyone by surprise, even Mojo Jojo./The Bare Facts: After Mojo kidnaps and blindfolds him, the Mayor has to rely on the girls' very different individual accounts of the crime to figure out exactly what happened.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2
description: Charlie tells some scary stories featuring the Bears and their friends.

He's in town for a high school reunion, but a terrible Fox Monster has attacked the reunion and kidnapped one of Mark's favorite old teachers. From reliving high school rivalries to surviving haunted, abandoned temples, Mark Hamill and our gang must face a ghastly Fox Monster in order to not only save the day, but their own lives.

title: The Vacation
description: The Wattersons set off on a relaxing vacation and end up running for their lives! The Wattersons are swapping scary stories on a family vacation, when their car breaks down in the middle of the desert. They are left with no alternative but to trust a complete stranger, whose appearance matches the scary guy in Mom's story. When the stranger brings them to a derelict gas station, just as he did in mom's made-up scary story, the Wattersons can no longer pretend the story isn't coming true . . .

title: Daycare/Joins the Circus/Afraid of the Dark/Friends/Visits the Doctor
description: It's Caillou's first day at daycare and he doesn't want to go./Caillou gets dressed all by himself./Caillou can't get to sleep./Caillou is talking to Grandma. She's surprised./Caillou has an ear infection.

description: When members of the Justice League are affected by the Phantom Zone ray and become phantom-like, their only hope for freedom is to somehow get a message to Booster Gold.

title: Spooky Boo
description: After Clarence leads a few neighborhood kids through his homemade haunted house, Chelsea suggests they go to the high school kids haunted house for some real scares. When the gang makes a wrong turn they find themselves in a mysterious house on a hill full of creepy sounds, ghoulish shadows and mutant rat men!

title: #IllusionsOfGrandeur
description: Ready to emerge from her father's shadow, Zee Zatara secretly seeks fame and acclaim performing for her own audience at the pier. But when her act is dismissed as fakery, she loses her cool and accidentally unleashes mischievous gremlins who run wild all over the pier.

title: Serpientastrofe
description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: El Club de Los Solitarios 2, La Isla de las Munecas
description: Para probar su valentía, Victor y Valentino se dirigen a una isla embrujada para recuperar una muñeca especial, pero Charlene y Piña están decididos a obtenerla antes que ellos.

title: Terror Tales of the Park
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: Bye Bye
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: A Night of Fright Is No Delight
description: Scooby must spend the night in a haunted house in order to receive an inheritance.

title: A Nightmare on Aberdale Street: Balance's Revenge
description: In this Halloween adventure, Clarence uses a special jack-o-lantern to enter the world of people's dreams. He discovers that something mysterious is causing his friends to have nightmares, and Clarence needs to stop it!

title: Fireworks
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Umbrella, Umbrella
description: Pocoyo finds an umbrella. He and his friends have great fun playing with the umbrella and trying to work out what it's for. When it starts to rain, Pocoyo - with the help of the children watching - realizes a perfect use for it!

title: Save the Fun Tree
description: Mush-Mush and friends' favorite play tree, the Fun Tree, is rotten and doomed. But Mush-Mush refuses to give up on it. In a last ditch effort to save the tree, our friends adventure off to try and track down the legendary Starmush, hoping his mysterious healing powers can save it.

title: That's Snow Ghost
description: A ski trip turns spooky for the gang when they run into the ghostly Yeti Beast and a Tibetan hermit, who says he is responsible for summoning the monster.

title: Problematic Prophecies
description: Elliott and Mo make a new friend, Nara, who has a very special ability.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Jacob del Arroyo
description: Un terrible corte de cabello obliga a Craig a visitar el Arroyo de encubierto.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Osos Padrinos
description: Los osos deben cumplir sus tareas de padrinos en la boda de Darrell.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: The New York Underground!
description: Our Shaggy is a bit of a Beatnik poet, and Scooby is so proud that he enters Shaggy into a poetry slam contest in Central Park. But when Shaggy finds out he's going up against famous singer-songwriter Halsey, he just about freaks. He freaks even more when the poetry slam is attacked by a horrible gator-man-monster from the New York City sewers below!

title: #FromBatToWorse
description: Having just moved to the boring Metropolis suburbs, Batgirl is thrilled when she intercepts a call from Batman asking for help. But before she can stop a visiting Gotham villain, she'll have to sneak past her dad, Police Commissioner Gordon.

title: Octi Evil/Geshundfight
description: Octi Evil: The heinous Him toys with Bubbles' mind by speaking to her through Octi, her favorite stuffed animal. Following Him's orders, Bubbles picks a fight with her sisters that lands them all in a time-out./Geshundfight: The Amoeba Boys' ill-conceived plan to stand in Townsville Park all night in the rain leaves them with a nasty virus that's really something to sneeze at.

title: Halloween
description: Carrie takes Gumball, Darwin and Anais to a real haunted house party on Halloween!

title: De Pesca
description: Durante un viaje de pesca, los osos son atacados por un enorme pez legendario.

title: Recuerdos de Bobby
description: Cuando un importante miembro de la comunidad del Arroyo se marcha, el trío lamenta su pérdida recordando los buenos tiempos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Big Show
description: Steven shoots a documentary that follows a local band as they get their first big break.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: Small World: Heart to Heartstone Part 4
description: In the stunning conclusion, the girls learn Lester has one more trick up his sleeve.

title: Taziator/Marvin Flag Gag: Little Martian/Climate Control
description: Bugs faces off against Taz in a Roman coliseum. Wile E. Coyote orders a weather control kit, but his chances of catching the Road Runner remain cloudy.

title: Mama Said
description: When King of Ooo sends Finn and Jake on a mission to catch flying mushrooms, they find their loyalty tested.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Terror Tales of the Park IV
description: The park guys try to keep Muscle Man awake with scary stories on a long drive so that they can meet his mom.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Be Cold, Scooby-Doo!
description: The gang hits the ski slopes, although Daphne's more focused on nailing Fred with a revenge snowball. Their snowy fun is soon interrupted by the appearance of an evil Snowman Monster eager to scare all trespassers off his mountain.

title: Tu mama y la mia
description: Steven lleva a Garnet a conocer a algunos de sus nuevos amigos.

title: Bumgorf
description: When the Titans realize they have not seen Silkie for a long time, they take turns guessing what happened to him.

title: Manzana es Bajito
description: Manzana tiene que ser alto para poder enamorarse.

title: Sausage and Sweetie Smash
description: Onion must stop Apple from falling prey to his obsession, but a certain phone game is proving to be quite an obstacle.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: A Secret Tweet
description: The babies plan a surprise birthday party for Tweety.

title: Princess Monster Wife
description: When Ooo's princesses start losing body parts left and right, Finn and Jake investigate.

title: Saga of the Swamp Beast
description: The gang's trip to the bayou is ruined by a shambling Swamp Beast that's scaring away anyone who dares to enter its soggy domain!

title: Sed de Poder
description: Axel y sus juguetes despliegan el Joyride en una batalla de "barco" a "barco" contra el Dr. Nautilus, quien ha perforado una tubería de agua para inundar las alcantarillas y se ha establecido como "Almirante Nautilus".

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Flower
description: When Gumball sees Leslie with Penny, he is overcome with uncontrollable jealousy.

title: Terror Tales of the Park II
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Algo Que Comi
description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de paseo al impenetrable Fort Knox, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo hace que un animal-mutante hambriento se enferme, iBen debe detenerlo antes de que se devore la reserva monetaria de la nación!

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: Ghoul Spirit
description: Gwen rejects the friendship of a friendly ghost.

title: He's the Sheriff
description: The gang struggles to get rid of the King when he joins them as their new deputy-for-a-day!

title: Terror Tales of the Park III
description: Each of the park guys want to win a bet by telling the scariest story at a Halloween party.

title: Under a Red Sun
description: Steppenwolf "boom tubes" Superman to a planet with a red sun in order to make the Man of Steel powerless. Somehow Batman and Big Barda have to locate the planet before Superman is destroyed.

title: Drum Roll Please
description: Pocoyo and his playmates love dancing to the Ball Orchestra's music. When it stops, they try to make their own band. Sleepy Bird's snoring sets the rhythm, and together they all make a wonderful, harmonious din.

title: Fear of the Fire Beast!
description: When Scooby and the gang are in Sicily, they're chasing a fire monster! But, they are surprised to meet up with none other than famous actor Steve Buscemi. His ancestors are from this area, and he has a lot of cousins in town and was just visiting. But, he's being plagued by fire monster attacks. Our gang teams up with Mr. Buscemi to get to the bottom of this fiery mystery. Let's hope Mr. Buscemi can train our gang to be proper fire fighters and mystery solvers, before they all get burned.

title: Stink. Stank. Stunk
description: When a skunk comes seeking its annual revenge on Chef, Duncan sees it as an opportunity to get a vacation from daycare.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Nos Equivocamos
description: iK.O., Rad y Enid rompen por accidente una de las preciadas posesiones del Sr. Gar!
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Jinxening
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP help a kid who's been jinxed and can't talk, but they soon come to regret it.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Witches Brew
description: The Titans throw a Halloween party and invite the Justice League but the witches brew Robin creates has side effects.

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple wants to experience love.

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: Jacob of the Creek
description: A terrible haircut forces Craig to go undercover at the Creek.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El Silbon
description: Víctor arma un laberinto de maíz embrujado, pero los chicos del pueblo creen que es muy malo. Vic decide hacer que el laberinto sea más aterrador con la ayuda de El Silbón para asustar de verdad a los chicos, pero El Silbón tiene sus propios planes.

title: Afraid of the Dark
description: When UG helps a little girl who is afraid of the dark, he convinces her there's nothing to be afraid of but their imaginations.  But when their imaginations prove to be pretty terrifying, they go on a quest to turn on the lights.

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: #DeMalEnPeor
description: Habiéndose mudado a los aburridos suburbios de Metrópolis, Batgirl se emociona cuando intercepta una llamada de auxilio de Batman. Pero antes de que pueda ir a detener a un villano visitante de Ciudad Gótica, Barbara debe escabullirse de su casa y de su padre, el comisionado Gordon.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Thirst for Power
description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

title: El Oso Troyano
description: Cuando Axel abre una caja de regalo de suscripción que ni siquiera ordenó, el equipo encuentra sus filas divididas por un oso robótico, io la Princesa SugarSalt disfrazada!

title: Brain Trust
description: Dr. Fox accidentally transports the gang inside her brain, where they must control her movements to complete a dangerous experiment.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Reunion en la Oscuridad
description: Axel debe ayudar a Bearbarian a superar su miedo secreto a la oscuridad para evitar que Dynamo le robe su viaje.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: The Bodyguard
description: When Don becomes part of Tez's Jaguar Patrol squad, Victor and Valentino are determined to get him fired by any means necessary.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Taz in Toyland
description: After Taz breaks all of his toys, Granny gives him one last chance to care for something.

title: Belson's Sleepover
description: Belson invites Clarence and friends to a sleepover party, with a catch: whoever can survive the night's pranks and scares will win Belson's old Acedia game system!

title: I Am Ice Bear
description: After Ice Bear hits his head, Grizz and Panda notice him acting like a different person.

title: Las Noticias Nunca Duermen
description: Lil 'Nelson toma un trabajo como repartidor de periódicos, lo cual es más difícil de lo que parece en una ciudad invadida por Pyro Vipers y una malvada hechicera serpentina.

title: Snaketastrophy
description: The Serpentine attack on NINJAGO City is seen from an unexpected perspective - entirely in the style of a live newscast delivered by Gayle Gossip and her cameraman.

title: Major Competition/Mr. Mojo's Rising
description: Major Competition: There's a new man in town, Major Man, a perfect superhero, who cuts in on the girls' turf. But the girls prove that even though they're minors, they're still the major part of saving the day./Mr. Mojo's Rising: Mojo kidnaps the Professor and forces him to give him the same superpowers at the girls. But once empowered, the true evolution of this supervillain chimp comes to light.

title: Fragmentos
description: Steven se dirige al bosque para entrenarse con un poderoso mentor.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Feed Me
description: The Titans release a small marshmallow ducky that the Easter Bunny had locked up, not knowing the danger they have unleashed.

title: Cutting Corners
description: Ben approaches Geezer Bob about doing a little yard work to earn spending money, but when Ben goes Upgrade to transform the lawnmower into a super fast mowing machine, he accidentally draws the ire of Bob's gnome-neighbors, the tiny, terrifyingly tenacious Billy-Bob Goblins.

title: New Pam in Town
description: When Pam is chased by a huge scary dinosaur, a concerned Seth invites her to live with him in Fungietown. Pam adapts to city living, but the Fungies' newfound love for Pam attracts attention, putting the entire town in danger!

title: The Scam
description: At Halloween show and tell, the class isn't buying Gumball's story about Gargaroth the Devourer until Carrie fakes a terrifying haunting. The kids convince the school to hire them as ghost exterminators and take their payment in Halloween candy. But when it turns out Gargaroth is real, suddenly Gumball is expected to be the town's savior.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Scared Silly
description: When the Rust Bucket runs out of gas on a foggy East Coast road, Ben, Gwen and Max are forced to stay at a hotel being menaced by Creepy Carl, a local folklore expert, who may actually be a ghost!

title: What a Boy Wonders
description: Robin forms a book club to debut his new autobiography, but the Titans would rather discuss other books.

title: Prince Starling's Quest
description: Lion-O is happily playing with Snarf in their "Frolicking Field" and doesn't have a care in the world, unfortunately he's accidentally stomping all over the miniature village of the Micrits! The tiny people want to defeat the "giant orange monster" but such a quest would require a brave hero. Luckily, the Micrits have such a hero: Prince Starling! Now, let us the tell you the epic tale of Prince Starling as he journeys to find the fountain of growth and defeat the wicked Lion-O, who has no idea any of this is going on!

title: #CrushingIt
description: Diana Prince is absolutely crushing it in every single aspect of life as a student at Metropolis High, until someone shows up who threatens to throw her off her game for good.

title: Thomas Blasts Off
description: It's rocket launch day and all the trains get to help deliver the big rocket parts, but when Thomas is assigned a tiny part, he puts it off to help the others with their more exciting parts, not realizing that his "small" task was just as important.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Las historias de Halloween de Charlie
description: Charlie es el presentador de unas historias de terror protagonizadas por los Osos.

title: To Balderly Go
description: Prohyas is crushed when his good hair day becomes a no hair day and Vambre has to battle a furry monster alone while her bro is in shock without his locks!

title: #BatallaEnElMuseo
description: Supergirl siempre confía en su fuerza, pero necesitará mas que músculos para impedir que la astuta Catwoman robe unas valiosas gemas del museo de ciencias.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.

title: One Minute Mysteries!
description: Scooby and Shaggy love hanging out with their very best eating buddy, Barry Allen aka the Flash. Barry is sad his two buddies always get pulled away from their food-fests to go solve mysteries. He decides to help our Mystery Solvers by solving their mysteries Flash-style so quickly our gang can't keep up. Our gang love and respect the Flash but they have a very specific way they like to solve mysteries.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Spoooooky Game
description: The gang's weekly board game night has been getting a little too competitive lately, so when Unikitty finds a spooky old board game that's clearly haunted, their desire to win gets turned upside down, but cursed or not, they'll be the first to the finish line!

title: Sorcerer Snacks Scare
description: Shaggy and Scooby discover their new favorite food as the gang investigates the mystery of a frightening Sorcerer that's haunting a snack factory!

title: Sobreviviendo A La Tormenta
description: El campamento de Ben y Gwen se ve interrumpido por los gélidos Weatherheads -Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o-, pero un Omnitrix que funciona mal y dispara un montón de extraterrestres podría no ser un pronóstico de éxito.

title: Ratar-O
description: The ThunderCats have gotten so good at defeating the Mutants of Plun-Darr that it's basically become routine. That all changes with the arrival of the Mutants' old leader: Ratar-O, wielder of the Sword of Plun-Darr! Uh-oh!

title: Nowhere to Hyde
description: The gang follows a mysterious figure through a marsh to the house of a latter-day Dr. Jekyll, whose alter ego is apparently a jewel thief.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.

title: Too Hot to Handle
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat so Lucas and his friends do whatever it takes to keep him from burning his mouth.
